snippet.title: Official Destiny: Rise of Iron Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Get fired up for Destiny: Rise of Iron, available on 9/20. Includes a new cinematic story campaign, new weapons and armor, a new Raid, new and remastered co-operative Strikes, a new social space, and more.
 
Pre-order Destiny: Rise of Iron and receive the Iron Gjallarhorn Exotic rocket launcher: https://www.destinythegame.com/wheretobuy
